Uses of Package
suncertify.ui

  • Packages that use suncertify.ui 
    Package Description
    suncertify.ui
    This package makes up the the presentation layer of the application.
  • Classes in suncertify.ui used by suncertify.ui 
    Class and Description
    AbstractWindow
    AbstractWindow is the common superclass of all frames used in the application and a subclass of JFrame.
    ClientWindow
    The class ClientWindow is direct subclass of AbstractWindow and acts as the main UI window for the application.
    ContractorModel
    ContractorModel extends the TableModel interfaces and specifies extra methods that the ContractorTable table will need for interacting with the custom contractor data model.
    LaunchManager
    LaunchManager defines useful method definitions for launching and configuring the application.
    WindowManager
    WindowManager is the common interface for all UI frames in the application.
